{
    "IgxAccordionComponent": {
        "comment": {
            "tags": {
                "igxmodule": {
                    "comment": {
                        "text": "IgxAccordionModule",
                        "tagName": "igxmodule"
                    }
                },
                "igxkeywords": {
                    "comment": {
                        "text": "accordion",
                        "tagName": "igxkeywords"
                    }
                },
                "igxgroup": {
                    "comment": {
                        "text": "Layouts",
                        "tagName": "igxgroup"
                    }
                },
                "remark": {
                    "comment": {
                        "text": [
                            "Ignite UI for Angular Accordion コンポーネントを使用すると、単一のコンテナーに表示された複数の縮小パネル間を移動できます。",
                            "Accordion は、基になるパネルの展開状態を制御するキーボード ナビゲーションと API を提供します。"
                        ],
                        "tagName": "備考:"
                    }
                },
                "example": {
                    "comment": {
                        "text": [
                            "```html",
                            "<igx-accordion>",
                            "  <igx-expansion-panel *ngFor=\"let panel of panels\">",
                            "      ...",
                            "  </igx-expansion-panel>",
                            "</igx-accordion>",
                            "```"
                        ],
                        "tagName": "例:"
                    }
                }
            },
            "shortText": "IgxAccordion は、複数の展開パネルを収容できるコンテナー ベースのコンポーネントです。"
        },
        "properties": {
            "id": {
                "comment": {
                    "tags": {},
                    "shortText": [
                        "アコーディオン コンポーネントの `id` を取得または設定します。",
                        "デフォルト値は `\"igx-accordion-0\"` です。",
                        "```html",
                        "<igx-accordion id=\"my-first-accordion\"></igx-accordion>",
                        "```",
                        "```typescript",
                        "const accordionId = this.accordion.id;",
                        "```"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "singleBranchExpand": {
                "comment": {
                    "tags": {},
                    "text": [
                        "```html",
                        "<igx-accordion [singleBranchExpand]=\"true\">",
                        "...",
                        "</igx-accordion>",
                        "```",
                        "```typescript",
                        "this.accordion.singleBranchExpand = false;",
                        "```"
                    ],
                    "shortText": [
                        "アコーディオンが投影される展開パネルの展開を処理する方法を取得/設定します。",
                        "`true` に設定すると、一度に展開できるパネルは 1 つのみで、その他のブランチはすべて縮小されます。"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "panelExpanding": {
                "comment": {
                    "tags": {
                        "remarks": {
                            "comment": {
                                "text": [
                                    "このイベントはキャンセルできます。",
                                    "```html",
                                    "<igx-accordion (panelExpanding)=\"handlePanelExpanding($event)\">",
                                    "</igx-accordion>",
                                    "```",
                                    "```typescript",
                                    "public handlePanelExpanding(event: IExpansionPanelCancelableEventArgs){",
                                    " const expandedPanel: IgxExpansionPanelComponent = event.panel;",
                                    " if (expandedPanel.disabled) {",
                                    "     event.cancel = true;",
                                    " }",
                                    "}",
                                    "```"
                                ],
                                "tagName": "備考:"
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "shortText": "パネルが展開される前に発生します。"
                }
            },
            "panelExpanded": {
                "comment": {
                    "tags": {},
                    "text": [
                        "```html",
                        "<igx-accordion (panelExpanded)=\"handlePanelExpanded($event)\">",
                        "</igx-accordion>",
                        "```",
                        "```typescript",
                        "public handlePanelExpanded(event: IExpansionPanelCancelableEventArgs) {",
                        " const expandedPanel: IgxExpansionPanelComponent = event.panel;",
                        " console.log(\"Panel is expanded: \", expandedPanel.id);",
                        "}",
                        "```"
                    ],
                    "shortText": "パネルが展開された後に発生します。"
                }
            },
            "panelCollapsing": {
                "comment": {
                    "tags": {
                        "remarks": {
                            "comment": {
                                "text": [
                                    "このイベントはキャンセルできます。",
                                    "```html",
                                    "<igx-accordion (panelCollapsing)=\"handlePanelCollapsing($event)\">",
                                    "</igx-accordion>",
                                    "```"
                                ],
                                "tagName": "備考:"
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "shortText": "パネルが縮小される前に発生します。"
                }
            },
            "panelCollapsed": {
                "comment": {
                    "tags": {},
                    "text": [
                        "```html",
                        "<igx-accordion (panelCollapsed)=\"handlePanelCollapsed($event)\">",
                        "</igx-accordion>",
                        "```"
                    ],
                    "shortText": "パネルが縮小された後に発生します。"
                }
            }
        },
        "methods": {
            "expandAll": {
                "comment": {
                    "tags": {},
                    "text": [
                        "```typescript",
                        "accordion.expandAll();",
                        "```"
                    ],
                    "shortText": "縮小されたすべての展開パネルを展開します。"
                }
            },
            "collapseAll": {
                "comment": {
                    "tags": {},
                    "text": [
                        "```typescript",
                        "accordion.collapseAll();",
                        "```"
                    ],
                    "shortText": "展開されたすべての展開パネルを縮小します。"
                }
            }
        },
        "accessors": {
            "animationSettings": {
                "getter": {
                    "comment": {
                        "tags": {},
                        "text": [
                            "```html",
                            "<igx-accordion [animationSettings]=\"customAnimationSettings\"></igx-accordion>",
                            "```",
                            "```typescript",
                            "const customAnimationSettings: ToggleAnimationSettings = {",
                            "     openAnimation: growVerIn,",
                            "     closeAnimation: growVerOut",
                            "};",
                            "this.accordion.animationSettings = customAnimationSettings;",
                            "```"
                        ],
                        "shortText": "パネルが展開/縮小時に使用するアニメーション設定を取得/設定します。"
                    }
                },
                "setter": {
                    "comment": {
                        "tags": {},
                        "text": [
                            "```html",
                            "<igx-accordion [animationSettings]=\"customAnimationSettings\"></igx-accordion>",
                            "```",
                            "```typescript",
                            "const customAnimationSettings: ToggleAnimationSettings = {",
                            "     openAnimation: growVerIn,",
                            "     closeAnimation: growVerOut",
                            "};",
                            "this.accordion.animationSettings = customAnimationSettings;",
                            "```"
                        ],
                        "shortText": "パネルが展開/縮小時に使用するアニメーション設定を取得/設定します。"
                    }
                }
            },
            "panels": {
                "getter": {
                    "comment": {
                        "tags": {},
                        "text": [
                            "```typescript",
                            "const panels: IgxExpansionPanelComponent[] = this.accordion.panels;",
                            "```"
                        ],
                        "shortText": "すべてのパネルを取得します。"
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}